```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant IGW as Internet Gateway
    participant NitroNW as Nitro Network Card
    participant SG as Security Group (hardware)
    participant EC2 as EC2 Instance

    Browser->>IGW: HTTP request to Public IP
    IGW->>NitroNW: VXLAN-encapsulated packet to physical host
    NitroNW->>SG: Check inbound rules
    Note over SG: Port 80 allowed? YES
    SG->>EC2: Deliver inner packet
    EC2->>SG: Response
    Note over SG: Stateful: return allowed automatically
    SG->>NitroNW: Forward
    NitroNW->>IGW: VXLAN decap
    IGW->>Browser: Response
```
